perplexity-health-researcher/
├── app.py                    # Main FastAPI application, API routes, and core logic
├── schemas.py                # Pydantic models for request/response data
├── services.py               # Contains Perplexity interaction, research orchestration, report structuring
├── templates/
│   └── index.html            # Basic HTML page for user interaction
├── static/
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css         # Basic CSS
│   └── js/
│       └── script.js         # JavaScript for frontend logic
├── .env                      # For API key (DO NOT COMMIT)
└── requirements.txt          # Python dependencies

in the .env file :
PERPLEXITY_API_KEY="your_actual_perplexity_api_key_here"
also create a virtual enviroment and then after that run pip install -r requirements.txt after this you have installed all the fucking libraries needed then run the venv and then run the app.py
Also dont use the live server instead go to the url http://127.0.0.1:8000/
